    <item>
      <title>Zelenskiy说，前线“沉默”应在停火之前</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/zelenskiy-says-frontline-silence-should-precede-ceasefire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统沃迪米尔·泽伦斯基（Volodymyr Zelenskiy）表示，在美国提议的30天停战开始之前，应在前线进行一段时间的“沉默”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/zelenskiy-says-frontline-silence-should-precede-ceasefire</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 13:04:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非提议较小的增值税以结束预算僵局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/south-africa-proposes-smaller-vat-hike-to-end-budget-impasse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非财政部长伊诺克·戈尼格瓦纳（Enoch Godongwana）提议扩大消费税的缩减和遏制支出，以赢得在先前的迭代被击落后，从美国脆弱的管理联盟中赢得对预算的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/south-africa-proposes-smaller-vat-hike-to-end-budget-impasse</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 12:06:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
